  <subsection xml:id="quadric-surfaces">
    <title>Quadric Surfaces</title>
    <p>
      In this section, we will look at a set of surfaces with algebraic equations that are quadratic in <m>x</m>, <m>y</m>, and <m>z</m>. This will give us a category of example surfaces that are algebraically simple but exhibit a variety of interesting characteristics.
    </p>
